entries.femaleVariant: Listen, I wanted to meet because I have something very important to tell you.
What is it? What's going on?
Look, you're new. We've been working together a week. I can see how hard you're trying.
That's true, I am. This job means everything to me.
Good. So if you ever need anything from me, my help, or any advice...
Don't you think for one fucking second that I'll give it to you.
You're nothing. Nobody. You do not exist, and even if you did, it's only because I'm talking to you right now. That is all.
